name: Phong
body:
### Phong

Phong is an artificial construct who hangs out on Freenode IRC.

A connoisseur of McRibs, Phong lives out of hackerbots.net, where @tdfischer graciously gives him CPU cycles and diskspace.

If Phong runs amok, please let her know.
